<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17477</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们的家附近有一条运河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>货船在运河上来来往往。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大部分货船上都载着煤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有些货船有发动机，有些货船需要用马拉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>和喜欢铁路一样，孩子们也很喜欢运河。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但他们更喜欢铁路，主要原因有两个：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个是他们先发现了铁路，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>另一个是运河上的人不是很友好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一次，孩子们在运河边钓鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61706</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个货船上的男孩儿为了找乐子，朝着菲利斯扔了一块煤。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61706</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>真是个淘气的男孩儿！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然菲利斯说自己没受伤，但是他们还是结束钓鱼回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77663</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这天天气晴朗，三个孩子沿着运河散步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得说：“我们再去钓鱼吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81931</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>菲利斯想起了那个淘气的男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93229</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是彼得说：“菲利斯，要是他再拿煤扔你，我就去打他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93229</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是他们沿着小路来到运河边，开始钓鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99253</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们钓了半个小时。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”一个声音大喊，“让开！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107316</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一匹白色的老马慢慢地向他们走来，它拉着一艘船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比、彼得和菲利斯急忙跳到旁边，爬上山坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125440</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们等着船和马经过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125440</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“船要停在这里，真倒霉！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>船上的男人看着他们，生气地说：“你们看什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139290</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们没有看你。”鲍比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就走开！”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142707</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们为什么不能留在这里？我们没有打搅任何人！”菲利斯说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152995</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们打搅我了！”男人说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从船上下来，向着孩子们走来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们有点儿害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人抓住彼得的腿说：“你们不能在运河里钓鱼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不然我就不客气了！“</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比走下来，对男人说：“请不要生气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174301</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们不会再钓鱼了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181849</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，那就快回家去！”男人回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181849</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人回到船里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184490</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛利亚，把外套给我！”他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个抱着小宝宝的红头发女人把外套扔给他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去‘玫瑰和王冠’酒吧，孩子睡了以后来找我。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人走了以后，孩子们走下山坡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我认为运河是大家的。”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人下了船，看到了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别把比尔说的话放在心上。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223987</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就是这样，不过他两个小时后才回来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227743</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以继续钓鱼了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。”鲍比说，“您很善良，您的孩子呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在船舱里睡着了。”她回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243217</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事，他在那里很安全，狗也和他在一起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243217</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>彼得又钓了一会儿鱼，但什么也没钓到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天黑了，女孩儿们有点儿累了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，菲利斯大喊：“快看那儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265859</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指着船舱。烟从门里冒出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>271673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个男人的船起火了，活该！”彼得说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>271673</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“彼得，你怎么能这么说？”菲利斯说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275899</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“想想那只可怜的狗吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有小宝宝！”鲍比突然尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282882</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289797</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>三个孩子飞快地向货船跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>